node.name: DBEclipse
node.shortdescription: Database browser plugin for Elipse for databases supported by JDBC. SQL-parser hyperlinks object references for convenient Transact-SQL source browsing just as you would the web site. Supports Sybase, SQLServer, Oracle and DB2.
